-- Moscow Apartment Sales Reach Record Last Year, Kommersant Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-01-13T06:32:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-13/moscow-apartment-sales-reach-record-last-year-kommersant-says.html
Apartment sales in Moscow reached a
record of 91,224 deals last year as prices stabilized and the
economy recovered,  Kommersant  reported, citing city statistics.  This was a 6.5 percent increase from 2010 and exceeded the
2003 level of 90,878 transactions, the newspaper said. The
average price rose 10 percent, the same as the previous year,
and reached $4,979 per square meter last year, according to
Kommersant.  To contact the reporter on this story:
